works.description: Last month, Car Design Fetish announced results for the Batmobile Design Competition, a design competition centered around the vehicle used by the Dark Knight in his Gotham-saving enterprises. Now, SideQuesting, a sister site of Car Design Fetish, has announced results for the design competition that asked to create a new concept for the Light Cycle vehicle from the Tron movie series. More than 100 works were submitted in less than 20 days for the Light Cycle Design Contest, from 3D renderings to pencil sketches. The competition was launched to celebrate the upcoming launch of Tron and Tron: Legacy on DVD and Blu-ray.
